title: Benihana is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA
statement: Benihana's website is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA accessibility standards, meaning some content does not fully conform.

citations.quote: Benihana is partially conformant with WCAG 2.1 level AA. Partially conformant means that some parts of the content do not fully conform to the accessibility standard.
